    "FinderSnap needs Accessibility permission to resize and reposition Finder windows. This is a one-time setup." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "FinderSnap 需要辅助功能权限来调整 Finder 窗口的大小和位置。这是一次性设置。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "FinderSnap 需要輔助使用權限來調整 Finder 視窗的大小與位置。這是一次性設定。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "FinderSnap requires Accessibility access to change Finder's window frame." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
